        <speech by="#3d2afb09-46bb-45b0-8cdb-90ba97b15ed0">
          <from>MR. MCNEIL</from>
          <p>MR. MCNEIL : Thank you, Mr. Speaker, and I want to be clear that at no time has the Liberal caucus ever suggested that there should be deregulation. What we allowed for was for competition to happen in a regulated market.</p>
