        <speech by="#0768c045-71ae-4890-b6be-c52eb783ee95">
          <from>THE PREMIER</from>
          <p>THE PREMIER : Mr. Speaker, we are three questions deep into Question Period and he's already reduced to rhetoric. That's because he has nothing left. He knows that it is this government that is standing up for its citizens, ensuring that we have stable, long-term energy prices so that this will become an economic advantage for the people of Nova Scotia.</p>
