          <from>MR. PORTER</from>
          <p>MR. PORTER : A market for the excess energy is key to helping that project get off the ground. Nova Scotia could benefit from moving that electricity through our province, but if there is no market willing to pay the premium price for electricity, then it becomes stranded here, forcing up power rates even more.</p>
